# PURPOSE
# ------------------------------------------------------------
Swarm Mode provides:
- Cross-repo architectural awareness  
- Coordinated release trains  
- Shared compliance evidence  
- Global risk register  
- Multi-repo FinOps optimization  
- Federated CxO dashboards  
