- services  
- dependencies  
- infra footprint  
- compliance level  
- testing posture  
- cost profile  

## 2. Global State Aggregation
Swarm Engine collects:
- architecture maps  
- risk vectors  
- compliance status  
- BEADS backlog  
- active incidents  
- release schedules  

## 3. Multi-Repo Coordination
Provides:
- dependency graph alignment  
- version synchronization  
- cascading release orchestration  
- cross-repo regression prediction  

## 4. Federated Compliance Mapping
Unified:
- SOC-2 evidence  
- ISO 27001 mappings  
- NIST 800-53 controls  

## 5. Global FinOps Optimization
Generates:
- shared cost heatmaps  
- infra consolidation strategies  
- multi-repo scaling recommendations  

